WEBVTT

00:04.705 --> 00:06.607
- AH,
IT'S THE BOYS I OWN.

00:06.640 --> 00:10.244
- GRIFFIN, DO YOU REMEMBER
THE DEAL YOU MADE WITH US?

00:10.278 --> 00:12.046
- THE ONE WHERE YOU CATCH
AND DESTROY MY CLONE,

00:12.080 --> 00:13.514
AND I BUY YOU ALL JET PACKS?

00:13.547 --> 00:14.648
- NO.

00:14.682 --> 00:17.285
- THE DEAL WHERE YOU LET US USE
YOUR MALIBU BEACH HOUSE

00:17.318 --> 00:19.820
FOR THE DAY IF WE GET
A NUMBER ONE RECORD.

00:19.853 --> 00:21.255
- BOOYAH.

00:21.289 --> 00:22.590
- IT'S TRUE.

00:22.623 --> 00:27.195
BIG TIME RUSH OFFICIALLY HAS
A NUMBER ONE RECORD...

00:27.228 --> 00:30.364
- I KERPLANKISTAN.

00:30.398 --> 00:33.101
- YOU NEVER SAID WHERE
IT HAD TO BE.

00:33.134 --> 00:34.568
- WELL PLAYED.

00:34.602 --> 00:35.569
- OH, YES.

00:35.603 --> 00:38.272
- NOW, THERE ARE TWO RULES
IN MY BEACH HOUSE.

00:38.306 --> 00:42.110
ONE, DON'T GO NEAR MY PRICELESS
MING VASE COLLECTION.

00:42.143 --> 00:46.280
TWO, DON'T EVEN LOOK
AT MY CAR COLLECTION.

00:46.314 --> 00:48.216
ENJOY, OR DON'T.

00:48.249 --> 00:49.250
I DON'T CARE.

00:49.283 --> 00:52.253
[upbeat guitar surfer music]

00:52.286 --> 01:00.294
*

01:13.141 --> 01:21.081
*

01:23.517 --> 01:26.220
- SWEET WAVE.
- BEEP, BEEP, BEEP, BEEP.

01:26.254 --> 01:27.721
- HOW LONG DO THEY DO THIS?

01:27.755 --> 01:30.858
- IT'S HARD TO SAY.

01:30.891 --> 01:32.826
- THEY ONCE DID IT
FOR THREE HOURS.

01:32.860 --> 01:36.664
- * AH, AH, AH-AH, OH

01:36.697 --> 01:38.532
- * MAKE IT COUNT,
PLAY IT STRAIGHT *

01:38.566 --> 01:40.501
* DON'T LOOK BACK,
DON'T HESITATE *

01:40.534 --> 01:44.638
- * WHEN YOU GO BIG TIME

01:44.672 --> 01:46.540
- * WHAT YOU WANT,
WHAT YOU FEEL *

01:46.574 --> 01:48.509
* NEVER QUIT
AND MAKE IT REAL *

01:48.542 --> 01:51.512
- * WHEN YOU ROLL BIG TIME

01:51.545 --> 01:52.813
- * OH-OH, OH-OH

01:52.846 --> 01:54.448
- * HEY, HEY

01:54.482 --> 01:56.484
- * LISTEN TO YOUR HEART NOW

01:56.517 --> 01:58.586
- * HEY, HEY

01:58.619 --> 02:00.488
- * DON'T YOU FEEL THE RUSH

02:00.521 --> 02:02.390
- * UH-OH, UH-OH

02:02.423 --> 02:03.491
* UH-OH, UH-OH

02:03.524 --> 02:04.492
- * OH

02:04.525 --> 02:05.859
- * GO AND SHAKE IT UP

02:05.893 --> 02:08.529
* WHATCHA GOTTA LOSE

02:08.562 --> 02:09.797
* GO AND MAKE YOUR LUCK

02:09.830 --> 02:12.600
* WITH THE LIFE YOU CHOOSE

02:12.633 --> 02:16.204
* IF YOU WANT IT ALL,
LAY IT ON THE LINE *

02:16.237 --> 02:20.741
* IT'S THE ONLY LIFE YOU GOT
SO YOU GOT TO LIVE IT BIG TIME *

02:23.777 --> 02:26.447
all: BEST BEACH DAY EVER.

02:26.480 --> 02:27.715
- SO DO YOU THINK
GRIFFIN WILL MIND

02:27.748 --> 02:28.882
THAT WE INVITED SOME FRIENDS?

02:28.916 --> 02:30.918
- NAH,
IT'S JUST A COUPLE PEOPLE.

02:30.951 --> 02:34.822
[together]
WHOO!

02:34.855 --> 02:36.524
- ALL RIGHT, CAMILLE.

02:36.557 --> 02:37.658
- HERE.
- JENNIFERS.

02:37.691 --> 02:38.692
- SO HERE.

02:38.726 --> 02:40.628
- GUITAR DUDE.

02:40.661 --> 02:43.497
- TODAY IT'S UKULELE DUDE.

02:43.531 --> 02:46.934
- OOH,
AND OUR MALIBU CHAUFFEUR.

02:46.967 --> 02:48.302
- HERE.
- OH.

02:48.336 --> 02:49.903
- JUST REMEMBER,
ANYBODY ASKS,

02:49.937 --> 02:52.940
I'M JUST TAKING YOU
TO THE AIRPORT.

02:52.973 --> 02:57.678
- WHOO!

02:57.711 --> 02:58.679
- NO, NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

02:58.712 --> 03:00.648
THAT IS NOT PROPER BEACHWEAR.

03:00.681 --> 03:03.317
- I HAVE TO DO RESHOOTS
FOR OUR BIG MOUNTAIN BLIZZARD

03:03.351 --> 03:04.618
MYSTERY EPISODE.

03:04.652 --> 03:06.554
- BUT IT'S
THE BEST BEACH DAY EVER,

03:06.587 --> 03:08.289
AND I BOUGHT A BEACH BLANKET,

03:08.322 --> 03:11.292
THAT WE WERE GONNA SIT ON
AND STUFF.

03:11.325 --> 03:16.397
- I'LL HAVE MY DRIVER GET ME OUT
THERE AS SOON AS WE'RE DONE,

03:16.430 --> 03:20.634
SO DON'T LET ANY BEACH BABES
TAKE MY SPOT ON THAT BLANKET.

03:20.668 --> 03:21.702
- I WON'T.

03:21.735 --> 03:23.904
- GOOD-BYE KISS?

03:27.875 --> 03:31.479
- ALL ABOARD THE MALIBU
BEACH PARTY PARTY BUSH.

03:31.512 --> 03:34.315
- YOU SAID "PARTY" TWICE.

03:34.348 --> 03:35.549
- YOU BET I DID.

03:35.583 --> 03:36.884
- LET'S ROLL.

03:36.917 --> 03:41.021
all: WHOO!

03:41.054 --> 03:43.791
- GOOD MORNING,
SWEETHEART.

03:47.328 --> 03:49.697
DID THEY NOT PUT SUNBLOCK ON
LIKE I TOLD THEM?

03:49.730 --> 03:53.434
- COVERED THEMSELVES
FROM HEAD TO TOE.

03:53.467 --> 03:55.669
- THEN WHY IS IT STILL SEALED?

03:55.703 --> 03:59.307
- IDIOTS.

03:59.340 --> 04:01.309
[upbeat guitar surfer music]

04:01.342 --> 04:03.844
- WHOO!

04:03.877 --> 04:06.013
- STOP!

04:06.046 --> 04:08.482
- SHE'S GOT SUNBLOCK.

04:11.652 --> 04:12.686
- STOP!

04:12.720 --> 04:15.489
- GO, GO, GO, GO, GO.

04:15.523 --> 04:18.359
- STOP, STOP, STOP, STOP,
STOP, STOP, STOP.

04:18.392 --> 04:19.360
HEY.

04:19.393 --> 04:20.428
ARGH.

04:20.461 --> 04:21.362
- WELL, I HAVE TO SAY, MOM,

04:21.395 --> 04:23.431
THAT'S THE CLOSET YOU'VE GOTTEN
IN YEARS.

04:23.464 --> 04:24.898
- I HAVE BEEN ENTRUSTED
BY PARENTS

04:24.932 --> 04:26.099
TO PROTECT THEIR CHILDREN,

04:26.133 --> 04:30.638
AND I WILL NOT EXPOSE THEM
TO THE HARMFUL RAYS OF THE SUN.

04:30.671 --> 04:31.639
TO THE BEACH.

04:31.672 --> 04:33.441
- OH,
I HATE THE BEACH,

04:33.474 --> 04:34.442
SALTWATER IN MY EYES,

04:34.475 --> 04:36.944
SEAGULLS DIVE-BOMBING
FOR YOUR CHEESE PUFFS.

04:36.977 --> 04:38.312
- CELEBRITY BEACH HOUSES,

04:38.346 --> 04:40.881
WHERE YOU COULD GET
AN AUTOGRAPH.

04:40.914 --> 04:43.551
- ON THIS CONTRACT NAMING ME
AS THEIR NEW MANAGER.

04:43.584 --> 04:45.319
I'M IN.

04:45.353 --> 04:46.454
- LET'S ROLL.

04:46.487 --> 04:49.490
- HEY, WHAT'S WITH THE
"EMERGENCY" SATURDAY MEETING.

04:49.523 --> 04:50.624
- BOY BLAST.

04:50.658 --> 04:53.427
AUGUST OF '97.

04:53.461 --> 04:57.565
AFTER THEIR FIRST ALBUM,
LIVIN' LARGE, HIT NUMBER ONE,

04:57.598 --> 05:02.035
THE CELEBRATED BY RENTING
A BEACH HOUSE IN MALIBU.

05:02.069 --> 05:03.170
- YEAH, SO.

05:03.203 --> 05:06.740
- WHILE THERE, THEY DISCOVERED
THE LAID-BACK LIFESTYLE

05:06.774 --> 05:10.911
OF BEACH BABES
AND ZERO NEED FOR FOOTWEAR.

05:10.944 --> 05:12.646
- YEAH, SO.

05:12.680 --> 05:15.916
- THEIR SECOND ALBUM,
LIVIN' AT THE BEACH,

05:15.949 --> 05:18.719
FAILED TO MAKE THE TOP 100.

05:18.752 --> 05:21.655
THEIR THIRD ALBUM,
IF YOU WANT US,

05:21.689 --> 05:24.558
WE'RE AT THE BEACH
AND NOT RECORDING,

05:24.592 --> 05:27.861
WAS THEIR LAST.

05:27.895 --> 05:29.062
- I THINK YOU'RE OVERREACTING.

05:29.096 --> 05:31.532
BIG TIME RUSH IS NOT BOY BLAST.

05:31.565 --> 05:34.902
- THAT'S WHAT I THOUGHT,
UNTIL I GOT THIS MESSAGE.

05:34.935 --> 05:36.904
- GUSTAVO,
WE'RE GOING TO MALIBU.

05:36.937 --> 05:38.739
[together]
AND WE'RE NEVER COMING BACK.

05:38.772 --> 05:39.840
WHOO!

05:39.873 --> 05:42.075
- OKAY, WELL,
WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO?

05:42.109 --> 05:46.747
- WE ARE GONNA TURN
THEIR BEST BEACH DAY EVER

05:46.780 --> 05:50.718
INTO THEIR WORST BEACH DAY EVER.

05:50.751 --> 05:53.554
[cackling]

05:56.089 --> 06:00.661
ROLL OUT.

06:00.694 --> 06:05.098
all: BEACH HOUSE.

06:07.668 --> 06:10.438
[seagulls squawking]

06:10.471 --> 06:13.641
BEACH!

06:13.674 --> 06:16.644
[upbeat guitar surfer music]

06:16.677 --> 06:24.618
*

06:26.554 --> 06:28.656
- BEST BEACH DAY EVER.

06:28.689 --> 06:32.593
*

06:32.626 --> 06:35.563
- HEY,
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?

06:35.596 --> 06:39.533
I HAVEN'T SEEN SO MANY
DANCING TEENS ON THIS BEACH

06:39.567 --> 06:41.068
SINCE THE '60s.

06:41.101 --> 06:42.736
GO ON, THERE.

06:42.770 --> 06:46.139
- OH, WE'RE TAKING OVER
THE BEACH HOUSE FOR THE DAY.

06:46.173 --> 06:50.110
- AHH, AND YOUR GIRL'S BUSY,

06:50.143 --> 06:53.481
BUT YOU'RE TRYING TO MAKE
THE BEST OF THINGS.

06:53.514 --> 06:54.582
- HOW DID YOU KNOW THAT?

06:54.615 --> 06:58.619
- BECAUSE I'M YOU
FROM THE FUTURE.

07:00.921 --> 07:03.156
- NO, NO, NO, NO, I'M J.D.

07:03.190 --> 07:07.528
I LIVE ABOUT FOUR HOUSES DOWN,
BUT THIS IS A MAGICAL BEACH.

07:09.597 --> 07:10.564
- REALLY?

07:10.598 --> 07:11.832
- OH, YEAH.

07:11.865 --> 07:16.604
ALL THE BEACH MOVIES IN HISTORY
WERE MADE ON THIS VERY BEACH.

07:16.637 --> 07:20.941
OH, THE STORIES FILLED
WITH MUSCLEMEN.

07:20.974 --> 07:23.677
- WHOO, HEY, BUDDY.

07:23.711 --> 07:25.779
HEY, OLD DUDE.

07:25.813 --> 07:30.518
- AND THE BIG KAHUNA
LOOKIN' FOR THAT PERFECT WAVE.

07:30.551 --> 07:31.785
- AND I WILL FIND IT.

07:31.819 --> 07:35.055
COWABUNGA.

07:35.088 --> 07:39.760
- AND MAD SCIENTISTS.

07:39.793 --> 07:43.697
[metal detector beeping]

07:43.731 --> 07:46.900
IN FACT, THE ONLY THING
THAT'S MISSING IS A BEACH BABE.

07:46.934 --> 07:48.602
- I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

07:48.636 --> 07:51.572
IT'S KENDALL KNIGHT
FROM BIG TIME RUSH.

07:51.605 --> 07:53.674
- OH--OHHH.

07:53.707 --> 07:55.142
- O-M-G.

07:55.175 --> 07:58.746
I AM ON A BEACH BLANKET
WITH KENDALL KNIGHT.

07:58.779 --> 08:00.714
- NOW,
THERE IS ONE MORE THING.

08:00.748 --> 08:01.782
- CAN I TAKE A PICTURE?

08:01.815 --> 08:02.950
- UH...
- OKAY.

08:02.983 --> 08:05.786
- BUT I CAN'T REMEMBER
WHAT IT WAS.

08:05.819 --> 08:07.921
- BIG SMILE.

08:07.955 --> 08:10.123
SERIOUS.

08:13.827 --> 08:15.663
- HELLO, LADIES.

08:15.696 --> 08:20.133
I DIDN'T SEE YOU GUYS THERE
ADMIRING MY MUSCLES.

08:20.167 --> 08:23.203
- CARLOS, WE'RE NOT HERE
BECAUSE WE LIKE YOU.

08:23.236 --> 08:27.708
- WE'RE HERE BECAUSE WE LIKE
FANCY MALIBU BEACH HOUSES.

08:27.741 --> 08:30.944
[metal clanging]

08:30.978 --> 08:33.781
- SO PLEASE MAINTAIN
A 5-FOOT RADIUS

08:33.814 --> 08:38.786
UNTIL YOU GET
A FANCY BEACH HOUSE.

08:38.819 --> 08:41.789
[metal detector beeping]

08:48.295 --> 08:51.699
- OHHH.

08:51.732 --> 08:53.667
WHOO, OHH, OHH.

08:53.701 --> 08:55.769
HEY, BUDDY.

08:55.803 --> 08:57.671
HOW MUCH MONEY CAN YOU FIND
WITH THAT THING?

08:57.705 --> 09:01.341
- I READ ONE GUY FOUND A RING
ON THE BEACH WORTH $50,000.

09:01.374 --> 09:03.811
- OHH-OHH-OHH.

09:03.844 --> 09:05.112
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

09:05.145 --> 09:06.814
- I NEED TO BUY A BEACH HOUSE.
- NO, FORGET IT.

09:06.847 --> 09:08.816
I HAVE TO PAY FOR MED SCHOOL.

09:08.849 --> 09:09.950
- OKAY,
HOW ABOUT THIS?

09:09.983 --> 09:13.687
I DO ALL THE DIGGING,
WHILE YOU SIP ON SOME LEMONADE,

09:13.721 --> 09:19.092
AND I'LL FAN YOU.

09:19.126 --> 09:21.929
- WELL,
THE BREEZE DOES FEEL NICE,

09:21.962 --> 09:24.698
AND I DO LIKE SIPPING LEMONADE.

09:24.732 --> 09:26.133
ALL RIGHT,
LET'S GET RICH, PARTNER.

09:26.166 --> 09:29.069
- HOO-HOO-HOO.

09:31.138 --> 09:32.305
- HELLO, TASTY WAVES.

09:32.339 --> 09:33.607
I'M JAMES DIAMOND.

09:33.641 --> 09:36.243
I'LL BE RIDING YOU TODAY.

09:39.046 --> 09:41.715
- JAMES IS GONNA SURF.

09:41.749 --> 09:43.116
HERE COMES A WAVE.

09:43.150 --> 09:46.620
OH, THAT'S A BIG WAVE.

09:46.654 --> 09:48.088
THAT'S A BIG WAVE.

09:48.121 --> 09:49.289
- AHHH!

09:49.322 --> 09:50.958
[wave crashing]

09:50.991 --> 09:53.961
[seagulls squawking]

09:53.994 --> 09:55.796
- [coughing]

09:55.829 --> 09:57.397
- WHAT--WHAT HAPPENED?

09:57.430 --> 10:00.000
- OH, YOU BIT IT BIG TIME,
DUDE,

10:00.033 --> 10:03.737
BUT THIS GIRL PULLED YOU OUT
OF THE WATER.

10:03.771 --> 10:06.139
- DID I NEED MOUTH-TO-MOUTH
RESUSCITATION?

10:06.173 --> 10:07.240
- NO.

10:07.274 --> 10:09.309
- DARN IT.
- COME ON.

10:09.342 --> 10:11.679
- [coughs]

10:11.712 --> 10:13.947
WELL,
IF YOU'RE GONNA SAVE MY LIFE,

10:13.981 --> 10:15.282
AT LEAST YOU CAN TELL ME
YOUR NAME.

10:15.315 --> 10:16.684
- OH, IT'S...

10:16.717 --> 10:17.384
[dolphin chirping]

10:17.417 --> 10:20.120
[coughing]

10:20.153 --> 10:21.154
IT'S ANNIE.

10:21.188 --> 10:25.358
- OH.

10:25.392 --> 10:28.361
[upbeat guitar surfer music]

10:28.395 --> 10:30.097
*

10:30.130 --> 10:32.132
- IT'S SUNBLOCK TIME.

10:32.165 --> 10:35.669
[together]
SHE'S GOT SUNBLOCK!

10:39.973 --> 10:42.843
- IT SAYS HERE RUSSELL BRAND
LIVES RIGHT NEXT DOOR.

10:42.876 --> 10:46.814
HE'D BE A PERFECT FIRST CLIENT
FOR KNIGHT MANAGEMENT.

10:46.847 --> 10:49.049
- PROMISE ME YOU WON'T BREAK
ANY HARASSMENT LAWS.

10:49.082 --> 10:50.951
- I WON'T IF YOU WON'T.

10:50.984 --> 10:53.420
- GOOD LUCK, SWEETHEART.

10:53.453 --> 10:57.357
[metal detector beeping]

10:57.390 --> 10:58.826
- GET SOMETHING.

10:58.859 --> 11:00.694
- OH, OH, I GOT SOMETHING.

11:00.728 --> 11:03.096
- YES! YES!

11:03.130 --> 11:04.932
- OH, OHHH.

11:04.965 --> 11:06.734
IT'S A GIANT SILVER EARRING.

11:06.767 --> 11:07.935
THIS THING MUST BE WORTH--

11:07.968 --> 11:09.737
- ARRGH!

11:09.770 --> 11:12.139
YOU BE ROAMIN' ME BEACH NOW?

11:12.172 --> 11:14.374
both:
YAAH! REAL PIRATE!

11:14.407 --> 11:17.711
- NOT JUST ANY PIRATE,
PATCHY THE PIRATE,

11:17.745 --> 11:20.047
THE SALTIEST,
SKULL-AND-BONESIEST,

11:20.080 --> 11:23.784
HOOK HANDIEST PIRATE TO
EVER SEARCH FOR BURIED TREASURE.

11:23.817 --> 11:25.318
both: BURIED TREASURE?

11:25.352 --> 11:28.455
- AH, THE TREASURE OF ME GREAT
GRANDPAPPY SCRATCHY THE PIRATE.

11:28.488 --> 11:31.358
I GOT HIS MAP RIGHT HERE.

11:31.391 --> 11:34.895
NOPE, NO, THAT'S A DOODLE OF ME
FINDING THE TREASURE.

11:34.928 --> 11:37.430
AH, AHHH.

11:37.464 --> 11:39.767
OOH, THAT'S A BONE.

11:39.800 --> 11:43.370
HERE YOU GO, BOYS.

11:43.403 --> 11:47.174
AHH,
A MAP TO A FABULOUS TREASURE

11:47.207 --> 11:51.344
MUCH TO LARGE FOR ONE MAN
TO SPEND ALONE.

11:52.946 --> 11:54.414
WELL, BYE, BOYS.

11:54.447 --> 11:57.317
EXCUSE ME.

11:57.350 --> 11:58.518
- OH, GOD.

11:58.551 --> 11:59.820
- PATCHY, ONE MINUTE.
- PATCHY.

11:59.853 --> 12:00.620
PATCHY, WAIT UP.

12:00.653 --> 12:03.390
- PATCHY,
WE WANT TO TALK TO YOU.

12:03.423 --> 12:05.025
- CHEESE.

12:05.058 --> 12:06.760
- OKAY, LAST ONE.
- OKAY, LAST ONE.

12:06.794 --> 12:07.727
YAY.

12:07.761 --> 12:09.396
- I MEAN, CARLOS, JAMES,
AND LOGAN ARE OKAY,

12:09.429 --> 12:12.866
BUT WHEN YOU SING,
IT'S LIKE YOU'RE SINGING TO ME.

12:12.900 --> 12:15.135
- I, UH...REALLY?
THAT'S COOL.

12:15.168 --> 12:16.837
- AND BOYFRIEND
IS MY FAVORITE SONG.

12:16.870 --> 12:20.507
IT'S PLAYING IN MY HEAD
RIGHT NOW.

12:20.540 --> 12:23.911
- COOL.
HEY, UH, SANDY IS IT?

12:23.944 --> 12:25.378
IT'S BEEN REALLY FUN
HANGING OUT,

12:25.412 --> 12:29.316
BUT I'VE GOT TO GO BACK UP
TO THE HOUSE FOR SOME THINGS.

12:29.349 --> 12:32.452
- OH, OKAY.

12:32.485 --> 12:33.987
BYE, KENDALL.

12:34.021 --> 12:38.025
- BYE.

12:38.058 --> 12:39.159
CALL ME.

12:39.192 --> 12:41.528
I PUT MY NUMBER, EMAIL,
AND SCUTTLEBUTTER ON YOUR PHONE.

12:41.561 --> 12:45.465
- OKAY, I WILL.

12:45.498 --> 12:48.468
- OH, OKAY, OKAY, OKAY, OKAY.

12:51.604 --> 12:53.473
- HELLO, SWEETHEART.

12:53.506 --> 12:54.842
DID YOU FORGET SOMETHING?

12:54.875 --> 12:56.409
- MOM,

12:56.443 --> 12:59.312
HOW COOL TO SEE YOU AT THE--
OH, NO.

12:59.346 --> 13:03.316
OH.

13:03.350 --> 13:05.385
- OH, YOU CAN RUN,
BUT YOU CAN'T HIDE,

13:05.418 --> 13:08.555
KENDALL DONALD KNIGHT.

13:08.588 --> 13:11.158
- [breathing heavily]

13:11.191 --> 13:15.062
BEST...BEACH DAY...EVER.

13:17.564 --> 13:20.200
- KENDALL,
I DID IT.

13:20.233 --> 13:22.469
I BROKE UP WITH MY BOYFRIEND,
SO WE CAN GO OUT.

13:22.502 --> 13:24.137
- * AH, AH, AH-AH, OH

13:24.171 --> 13:30.177
- SANDY...SANDY...SANDY.

13:30.210 --> 13:32.445
- SANDY, NO.
OKAY, OFF, OFF, OFF, OFF, OFF.

13:32.479 --> 13:35.182
SANDY,
YOU'RE A REALLY SWEET GIRL,

13:35.215 --> 13:36.850
BUT I ALREADY HAVE A GIRLFRIEND.

13:36.884 --> 13:38.986
- I KNOW, ME.

13:39.019 --> 13:40.520
CHECK OUT
YOUR SCUTTLEBUTTER PAGE.

13:40.553 --> 13:43.056
I UPDATED YOUR STATUS
AND YOUR PHOTOS.

13:43.090 --> 13:44.224
- OH, THIS IS BAD.

13:44.257 --> 13:48.161
[phone ringing]

13:48.195 --> 13:50.330
HEY, YOU.

13:50.363 --> 13:52.632
- WHO WAS THAT ON
THE BEACH BLANKET KISSING YOU?

13:52.665 --> 13:55.635
- NOT MY NEW GIRLFRIEND,
BECAUSE YOU ARE MY GIRLFRIEND.

13:55.668 --> 13:58.638
ME ONLY LIKE YOU--

13:58.671 --> 14:00.941
- HE LOVES ME NOW, JO.

14:00.974 --> 14:04.144
BYE.

14:04.177 --> 14:05.578
WHEW,
THAT WAS AWKWARD.

14:05.612 --> 14:08.949
- SANDY, GIVE ME THE PHONE,
SO I CAN CALL JO

14:08.982 --> 14:12.252
AND STRAIGHTEN THINGS...

14:12.285 --> 14:16.289
- OH, KENDALL, THERE IS
NO NEED TO HIDE FROM OUR LOVE.

14:19.526 --> 14:21.061
- HELP.
- KENDALL, COME BACK.

14:21.094 --> 14:22.229
I LOVE YOU.

14:22.262 --> 14:24.164
[together]
OOOH, NEW GIRL.

14:24.197 --> 14:26.967
- NOW,
THIS MAP HAS BEEN IN MY FAMILY

14:27.000 --> 14:29.036
FOR HUNDREDS OF YEARS,
AND IT'S SPECIAL.

14:29.069 --> 14:30.437
- YEAH, BLAH, BLAH.
WHERE'S THE GOLD?

14:30.470 --> 14:33.406
- OHH, 'CAUSE I'VE GOT TO BUY
MY BEACH HOUSE.

14:33.440 --> 14:35.175
- I HAVE NO IDEA.

14:35.208 --> 14:36.643
NO ONE IN THE FAMILY
COULD EVER READ

14:36.676 --> 14:40.447
ITS STRANGE MOON MAN LANGUAGE.

14:40.480 --> 14:41.581
- YEAH,
IT'S UPSIDE DOWN.

14:41.614 --> 14:43.083
- ARE YOU SERIOUS?

14:43.116 --> 14:45.652
OHH.

14:45.685 --> 14:48.555
- "IF YOU SEEK
THIS RICH TREASURE OF MINE,

14:48.588 --> 14:52.459
SEARCH THE BEACH
WHERE THE SUN DON'T SHINE?"

14:52.492 --> 14:54.261
- TREE ON THE BEACH.
- TREE ON THE BEACH.

14:54.294 --> 14:56.463
- THAT'S IT.
GO, GO, GO, GO, GO.

14:56.496 --> 14:58.265
- IT'S A BEACH TREE,
BEACH TREE.

14:58.298 --> 14:59.299
IT'S A BEACH TREE.

14:59.332 --> 15:00.968
[together]
NEW GIRL.

15:01.001 --> 15:02.135
TREASURE!

15:02.169 --> 15:04.071
- WHOO!
- TREASURE, TREASURE, TREASURE.

15:04.104 --> 15:06.473
- YOU MUST BE
A REALLY STRONG SWIMMER

15:06.506 --> 15:08.141
TO PULL ME ALL THE WAY
INTO SHORE.

15:08.175 --> 15:12.545
- WELL, YOU COULD SAY
I GREW UP IN THE WATER.

15:12.579 --> 15:14.447
- WELL,
HOW ABOUT SOME LUNCH?

15:14.481 --> 15:15.949
OH, I CAN STEAM UP
SOME OF THESE CLAMS.

15:15.983 --> 15:17.450
- OH, NO, NO, NO.
DON'T BOTHER.

15:17.484 --> 15:20.553
I LIKE THEM RAW.

15:20.587 --> 15:22.055
- AHH!

15:22.089 --> 15:25.225
COULD YOU EXCUSE ME
JUST FOR A MINUTE?

15:28.628 --> 15:30.030
- OH, HEY, JAMES.
WHAT'S UP?

15:30.063 --> 15:31.498
WH--WH--WHERE ARE WE GOING?

15:31.531 --> 15:34.201
WHAT--WHAT...
HEH, WHAT...

15:34.234 --> 15:35.435
- WHAT WOULD YOU SAY
IF I TOLD YOU

15:35.468 --> 15:39.639
THAT THE GIRL WHO SAVED MY LIFE
EARLIER TODAY IS A MERMAID?

15:41.474 --> 15:43.176
- I WOULD SAY
THAT I PLAYED A MERMAID

15:43.210 --> 15:45.412
IN MERTEENS 4:
ESCAPE FROM SEAQUARIUM,

15:45.445 --> 15:49.482
AND IT MADE A VERY COMPELLING
CASE THAT MERMAIDS ARE REAL.

15:49.516 --> 15:52.452
[dolphin chirping]

15:55.388 --> 15:57.257
- SO HOW DO I FIND OUT?

15:57.290 --> 15:59.059
- WELL, IN THE MOVIE,
MERMAIDS ON LAND

15:59.092 --> 16:00.393
HAVE TO AVOID GETTING WET,

16:00.427 --> 16:04.231
BECAUSE THEY WOULD IMMEDIATELY
SPROUT A TAIL.

16:04.264 --> 16:06.766
- SO ALL I HAVE TO DO
IS GET HER DOWN TO THE BEACH

16:06.799 --> 16:08.068
AND GET HER WET.

16:08.101 --> 16:11.071
- NOT WITHOUT SUNBLOCK
YOU'RE NOT.

16:11.104 --> 16:14.607
- MRS. KNIGHT,
LOVELY TO SEE YOU, AND, UH...

16:14.641 --> 16:16.276
DANCE PARTY!

16:16.309 --> 16:19.279
[upbeat guitar surfer music]

16:19.312 --> 16:27.020
*

16:27.054 --> 16:28.155
- [gasps]

16:28.188 --> 16:29.522
OH, IT'S ON.

16:38.598 --> 16:40.233
- MARVIN, I'M GONNA HAVE TO
TURN AROUND NOW.

16:40.267 --> 16:41.634
I'M BEING TAPPED.

16:41.668 --> 16:45.672
- DOWN HERE.

16:45.705 --> 16:48.208
- HELLO.

16:48.241 --> 16:49.376
CAN I HELP YOU WITH SOMETHING?

16:49.409 --> 16:51.211
- NO, BUT I CAN HELP YOU.

16:51.244 --> 16:53.213
KATIE KNIGHT,
KNIGHT MANAGEMENT.

16:53.246 --> 16:54.581
- OH, THAT'S CHARMING.

16:54.614 --> 16:56.083
WHAT, DO YOU WANT IN AUTOGRAPH
OR SOMETHING LIKE THAT?

16:56.116 --> 16:57.217
IS THIS AN AUTOGRAPH?

16:57.250 --> 16:59.386
- YES,
ON THIS TALENT CONTRACT

16:59.419 --> 17:01.621
GIVING ME THE AUTHORITY
TO TAKE YOUR CAREER

17:01.654 --> 17:02.789
INTO THE STRATOSPHERE.

17:02.822 --> 17:04.324
- THAT'S CHARMING.

17:04.357 --> 17:06.126
JUST--JUST ONE MOMENT.

17:06.159 --> 17:08.228
MARVIN, YOU PROMISED
TO ORGANIZE A PARTY,

17:08.261 --> 17:09.262
AND IT'S NOT GOING WELL.

17:09.296 --> 17:10.330
I'VE GOT NO CHAIRS.

17:10.363 --> 17:13.300
I'VE NOT GOT ANY ICE SCULPTURES,
AND WORST OF ALL,

17:13.333 --> 17:15.602
THERE IS NO CENTERPIECE.

17:15.635 --> 17:17.104
I'M ANGRY, MARVIN.

17:17.137 --> 17:22.109
NOW, KATIE,
I NEED YOU TO STUDY HARD,

17:22.142 --> 17:24.644
GO TO COLLEGE,
AND THEN COME BACK HERE,

17:24.677 --> 17:26.213
AND WE'LL DISCUSS THINGS THEN.

17:26.246 --> 17:29.482
- OH,
I'LL BE BACK SOONER THAN THAT.

17:29.516 --> 17:30.583
- OKAY--WHOA, WHOA.

17:30.617 --> 17:33.686
EXCUSE ME, WHERE ARE
THE VEGETARIAN COCKTAIL WEENIES?

17:33.720 --> 17:35.488
- NOBODY ORDERED
COCKTAIL WEENIES.

17:35.522 --> 17:38.591
- HEY, I SPECIFICALLY ASKED
FOR VEGETARIAN COCKTAIL WEENIES.

17:38.625 --> 17:39.259
I HAD A DREAM.

17:39.292 --> 17:40.693
I WANT WEENIES AT MY PARTY.

17:40.727 --> 17:43.263
ALL MY PARTIES
ARE TO BE FULL OF WEENIES.

17:43.296 --> 17:46.233
- REMEDY IT.

17:49.636 --> 17:50.870
- OKAY, HERE'S THE PLAN.

17:50.903 --> 17:55.542
YOUR SENSE OF SMELL IS DIRECTLY
CONNECTED TO YOUR MEMORY, RIGHT?

17:55.575 --> 17:58.511
- RIGHT,
OR WE COULD FORGET THE PLAN

17:58.545 --> 18:00.213
AND GO HAVE A FUN DAY
AT THE BEACH.

18:00.247 --> 18:01.214
- NO.

18:01.248 --> 18:03.816
NOW, ALL WE HAVE TO DO
IS RELEASE THIS BARRAGE

18:03.850 --> 18:06.353
OF STINK BOMBS
IN GRIFFIN'S HOUSE.

18:06.386 --> 18:09.156
THAT WAY,
WHEN BTR THINKS OF THE BEACH,

18:09.189 --> 18:11.158
ALL THEY'RE THINK IS STINK.

18:11.191 --> 18:12.825
- AND NEVER WANT TO RETURN.

18:12.859 --> 18:16.663
- NOW, GET THE BACK DOOR.

18:16.696 --> 18:17.897
- AHH!

18:17.930 --> 18:20.567
[loud explosions]

18:20.600 --> 18:21.468
AHHH!

18:21.501 --> 18:22.469
LET ME OUT.

18:22.502 --> 18:23.836
- UNLOCK THE DOOR.

18:23.870 --> 18:28.175
- I CAN'T SEE THE DOOR.

18:28.208 --> 18:30.477
- AHH, I CAN TASTE IT.

18:34.181 --> 18:35.148
- HEY.

18:35.182 --> 18:37.484
[together]
AHH!

18:37.517 --> 18:38.918
- THERE'S A CRAZY FAN GIRL
WHO'S AFTER ME,

18:38.951 --> 18:40.520
WHO THINKS
SHE'S MY NEW GIRLFRIEND,

18:40.553 --> 18:41.654
SO HELP ME GET RID OF HER,

18:41.688 --> 18:45.825
BECAUSE I BROUGHT YOU
TO THIS BEACH HOUSE, AND PLEASE.

18:45.858 --> 18:48.161
[together]
FINE.

18:48.195 --> 18:49.862
- KENDALL.

18:49.896 --> 18:53.300
KENDALL.

18:53.333 --> 18:54.634
- ANYTHING?

18:54.667 --> 18:56.503
- OHH,
I'M GETTING SOMETHING.

18:56.536 --> 18:58.505
YES,
I'M GETTING SOMETHING.

18:58.538 --> 19:00.373
[fart noise]

19:00.407 --> 19:02.475
- [laughs]
HE GOT IT.

19:02.509 --> 19:05.545
- NO, NO, NO, THAT WAS NOT ME.

19:05.578 --> 19:08.881
IT WAS THIS.

19:08.915 --> 19:10.650
- AN OLD PIRATE WHOOPEE CUSHION?

19:10.683 --> 19:11.284
- THAT'S IT?

19:11.318 --> 19:13.320
THAT'S ME FAMILY TREASURE?

19:13.353 --> 19:14.421
OH, WHAT A RIP.

19:14.454 --> 19:17.357
- OH, W-W-WAIT, WAIT, WAIT,
IT HAS WRITING ON IT.

19:17.390 --> 19:19.426
"IF YE FOUND ME CUSHION
THAT OF POO,

19:19.459 --> 19:21.628
WALK 90 PACES SOUTH
FOR YOUR NEXT TREASURE CLUE."

19:21.661 --> 19:22.929
- OHH.

19:22.962 --> 19:24.464
IT'S NOT A TREASURE MAP.

19:24.497 --> 19:25.532
IT'S A TREASURE HUNT.

19:25.565 --> 19:28.501
- HA-HA, SOUTHWARD-HO, BOYS.

19:28.535 --> 19:29.469
ONE, TWO...

19:29.502 --> 19:31.638
- THAT'S WEST.

19:31.671 --> 19:33.506
- I KNEW THAT.

19:33.540 --> 19:37.477
[together]
ONE, TWO, THREE...

19:37.510 --> 19:41.648
- OH, SANDY,
THERE YOU ARE.

19:41.681 --> 19:43.283
- WHO ARE THEY?

19:43.316 --> 19:46.519
- HONEY, YOU CAN'T EXPECT
A ROCK STAR, LIKE KENDALL,

19:46.553 --> 19:48.755
TO HANG WITH ONE GIRL.

19:48.788 --> 19:51.524
- SO GET USED TO IT.

19:51.558 --> 19:53.826
- O-M-G.

19:53.860 --> 19:55.928
YOU'RE KENDALL KNIGHT.

19:55.962 --> 19:57.730
CAN I BE ONE OF YOUR MANY
CRAZED FAN GIRLFRIENDS

19:57.764 --> 19:59.632
THAT YOU CAN'T COMMIT TO?

19:59.666 --> 20:01.868
- BOOM.

20:01.901 --> 20:03.970
AHH, WHAT CAN I SAY?

20:04.003 --> 20:06.373
I'M SELFISH,
SPOILED CELEBRITY JERK FACE,

20:06.406 --> 20:08.708
WHO YOU PROBABLY WANT TO DUMP
RIGHT NOW.

20:08.741 --> 20:10.310
- OH, KENDALL.

20:10.343 --> 20:12.479
I KNOW YOU'RE JUST DOING THIS
TO MAKE ME JEALOUS,

20:12.512 --> 20:15.882
BUT I'M NOT THE JEALOUS TYPE,
BUT I WONDER IF JO IS?

20:15.915 --> 20:17.250
[camera shutter clicking]

20:17.284 --> 20:21.488
- OH, NO, NO, NO,
DON'T POST THE PICTURE.

20:21.521 --> 20:22.889
[phone rings]

20:22.922 --> 20:24.591
- HELLO.

20:24.624 --> 20:26.893
IT'S JO.

20:26.926 --> 20:30.597
- OH, NOW YOU'VE GOT ALL THE
JENNIFERS ON YOUR BEACH BLANKET.

20:30.630 --> 20:32.765
- LOOK, JO,
I CAN EXPLAIN EVERYTHING.

20:32.799 --> 20:35.968
THIS CRAZY FAN...

20:36.002 --> 20:38.738
- HE HUNG UP AGAIN.

20:38.771 --> 20:41.474
- HEY.

20:41.508 --> 20:44.644
YOU OWE ME A NEW PHONE.

20:44.677 --> 20:49.549
- BEST BEACH DAY EVER.

20:49.582 --> 20:51.651
- WAIT.
KENDALL, WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

20:51.684 --> 20:54.587
YOU'RE MY NEW BOYFRIEND.

20:54.621 --> 20:57.524
KENDALL.

20:57.557 --> 20:59.559
