21:49.576 --> 21:52.379
* BIGGER THAN
THE TWILIGHT LOVE AFFAIR *

21:52.412 --> 21:54.481
* I'LL BE HERE,
GIRL I SWEAR *

21:54.514 --> 21:55.415
