[together]
OOH, AHH, OHH.

22:49.602 --> 22:50.937
- OHH, MAMA KNIGHT.

22:50.970 --> 22:53.740
- WELL,
MY WORK HERE IS DONE.

22:53.773 --> 22:55.508
IF YOU NEED ME,
I'LL BE ON A BEACH CHAIR

22:55.542 --> 22:57.510
CATCHING UP ON MY READING.

23:01.814 --> 23:04.016
- CAN THIS DAY GET ANY WORSE?

23:04.050 --> 23:06.118
- KENDALL, AH, THERE YOU ARE.

23:06.152 --> 23:08.688
I JUST REMEMBERED
WHAT I FORGOT.

23:08.721 --> 23:12.425
A BAD GUY ALWAYS SHOWS UP
HALFWAY THROUGH THE MOVIE

23:12.459 --> 23:14.026
TO BEAT YOU UP.

23:14.060 --> 23:16.996
- WHAT?

23:19.632 --> 23:24.604
- SO YOU'RE THE DEAD MAN
WHO STOLE MY SANDY.

23:24.637 --> 23:27.874
PREPARE TO GET PUMMELED.

23:27.907 --> 23:29.542
- I TOLD YOU IT WAS
A MAGICAL BEACH.

23:29.576 --> 23:33.412
- * AH, AH, AH-AH, OH

